RESOLUTION

HP has provided the following upgrades to resolve these vulnerabilities. 
The upgrades are available from the following location: 

URL: http://software.hp.com 

Note: HP-UX Web Server Suite v3.05 contains HP-UX Apache-based Web Server v2.2.8.04 and HP-UX Tomcat-based Servlet Engine 5.5.27.02 
Note: HP-UX Web Server Suite v2.25 contains HP-UX Apache-based Web Server B.2.0.59.10 and HP-UX Tomcat-based Servlet Engine 5.5.27.02 

Web Server Suite        HP-UX                              Apache 
